hopobject.body: I'll send you a text parlodel nel bodybuilding Commander Neil Basu of the Metropolitan Police replied: "Until I received your letter on July 30 I had not seen or been copied into lists A and B provided to you by Soca. I contacted Soca that afternoon and they responded quickly providing me with a copy of that list that evening under the same conditions that it has been provided to you. Therefore, the MPS (Metropolitan Police Service) had possession of the list at 7pm on July 30.
